{"tid":1838700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳門十所高等院校宣佈延至2月11日或之後開學","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T06:47:08.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49b4b09cacea806f1d4bf827111f584fe597d01f","tid":1838700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:21:59.000Z","msg":"澳門至今有兩宗新型冠狀病毒感染個案。教育暨青年局宣布，因應疫情，非高等教育學校在農曆新年假期後，延至2月10日或之後上課，已通知學校妥善安排學生在家學習的相應方案，私立補充教學輔助中心及持續教育機構同時亦應配合，即延至下月10日或之後運作。<br />\n<br />\n另外，澳門大學等十所高等院校，以及非本地高等教育課程協辦機構，亦延後至2月11日或之後才開學。涉及的十所高等院校包括澳門大學、澳門理工學院、澳門旅遊學院、澳門保安部隊高等學校、澳門科技大學、澳門城市大學、聖若瑟大學、澳門鏡湖護理學院、澳門管理學院，及中西創新學院。<br />\n<br />\n高等教育局表示，會繼續密切留意疫情的最新發展，並與各高等院校保持緊密溝通，適時作出相關應對措施，以保障大專學生的生命安全，又提醒大專學生春節期間，如非必要，應減少外出。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504601-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504601-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=af94da72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504601-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=efbacbb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504601-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a220d371b8d2654a8a9fcc1309b51bd4e6fbc89f","tid":1838700,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"連大專院校都延後埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146a8380449dba917b1494a30c3ee84788321ac7","tid":1838700,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"呢D 先係抗疫，做野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"aa4887a9c6edc4be37ab3d9b8d188b272edfb8c3","tid":1838700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1bf82bddc817a776d8d75ac37293d8c0e5d5ca","tid":1838700,"uid":110583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a713a4839d4d89a7fa0a47d4eacc9620df5a2e","tid":1838700,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"慘過返澳門"}]}